{"type": "article", "id": 9555, "title": "废旧电池变移动电源", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-14T07:14:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235456Y53R98JlZNhafAQS.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t现代人换手机频繁，每年都有大量的的旧手机产生，而电池也往往会随着手机一起变为废品。废旧的电池既造成浪费，又污染环境。于是设计师 Kiyong Shin 推出了这款叫做 “Better Re” 的产品（既和电池的英文同音，又暗含回收使用的含义）。我们只需要把废旧的电池放在设计好的槽中，就可以把废旧电池变为一个移动电源。而多个废旧电池并在一起，便可以增加移动电源的供电能力。目前这款产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/betterre/better-re-upcycling-power-pack-reusing-smartphone\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以支持他们。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235452O2VIlqARBcm5teW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64547677\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235452Qr4oPSUHfNqBtkl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64547677\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354539yIUL4HgJ87Bi6Zs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.40709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235453tUT5iKPRNOpnX6Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73227384\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235454lBrocEiw1Uat8Hxd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73227384\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354548IEQM3SOYvobVkpZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235455ZgOHdXkJ0CBzu8e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.52567237\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235455WEI8QcSPHz5tmB2D.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235455AQbR01hvVUrTPl4w.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.78239609\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}